name: Norwegians
text:
Norwegians
"The Norwegians are leaving.The Norwegians are leaving.The Norwegians are gone."
 ―Julie Duvic
In February 1989, a group of Norwegian businessmen led by Sven Jorgenson and accompanied by an interpreter visited Twin Peaks, Washington to invest in the Horne Development Corporation's Ghostwood Development Project.
However, they hastily changed their plans after they learned from Audrey Horne about Laura Palmer’s death.
